{"tid":580963,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好辛苦 分手邊緣","createTime":"2018-03-05T02:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T13:49:03.000Z","uid":32841,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"319a9d10e6c3523bd9c8b25ad47c94c041779f32","tid":580963,"uid":32841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T02:35:48.000Z","msg":"我同女朋友其實都三年<br />\n有時關係會好差<br />\n我覺得佢脾氣大<br />\n佢又覺得我脾氣大 當然我認我脾氣真係大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早一個星期我好多野煩 好大壓力<br />\n屋企人過身 又同屋企人炒大鑊差啲開拖<br />\n公司又忙到仆街 仲要衰左單野差啲收埋warning<br />\n少左好多理佢 掛住搵朋友<br />\n因為有時覺得佢未做過fulltime唔知職場壓力掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到星期四 我發現佢同個男仔講野好曖昧<br />\n之後嘈到要分手 依加凍戰中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過又係嘅 我脾氣又大 控制慾又強 又成日冷落左佢，我怪得邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbb9309d87b5e7eb2906d6691cb555dedf3dd2e","tid":580963,"uid":151664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T02:43:28.000Z","msg":"師兄 帶帽好襯你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf2afc5dddc39587e71ebbcfd0f0d414c210a26","tid":580963,"uid":170755,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T02:46:50.000Z","msg":"大男人冇撚用"},{"pid":"d0c9ff812131c6936a6828b9b2be5f18b4309f63","tid":580963,"uid":154131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T02:49:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0dbcfdf893afe69dfcb0fa1d816d592f1f5b6ec8","tid":580963,"uid":32841,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T02:52:38.000Z","msg":"份情人節禮物仲未俾到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢依加都唔願同我講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3cb2b79c7d7db260df726ff1cd5078b4f37b4fa","tid":580963,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T02:54:12.000Z","msg":"送俾人啦<br />\n脾氣差死罪黎<br />\n除時玩死自己"},{"pid":"104453104094edef1e93b483030be60cdfffba64","tid":580963,"uid":32841,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T02:54:59.000Z","msg":"情人節個排要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一有假放個時又新年<br />\n結果買到個時都2x號<br />\n如果佢早啲收到份禮物結果會唔會有分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c17c8cb63b0726eb35c16c1ee6fe8d80f747da","tid":580963,"uid":135436,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T03:00:58.000Z","msg":"話曬都3年感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不如三口六面講清楚 有時女人都係想有人關心下 佢未必幫到手但你願意分享佢會好肯聆聽 脾氣對方都講到出聽話你大 咁你就改下 大家遷就吓包容吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過 如果閣下已經帽咗 咁就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64813c54c825cc0c6f74573b098f53752f700a6f","tid":580963,"uid":32841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"85c17c8cb63b0726eb35c16c1ee6fe8d80f747da","tid":580963,"uid":135436,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T03:00:58.000Z","msg":"話曬都3年感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不如三口六面講清楚 有時女人都係想有人關心下 佢未必幫到手但你願意分享佢會好肯聆聽 脾氣對方都講到出聽話你大 咁你就改下 大家遷就吓包容吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過 如果閣下已經帽咗 咁就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T03:03:08.000Z","msg":"佢一句都唔應我了已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有得點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727cb388c726d8b50998facf3fa7a435186d6993","tid":580963,"uid":32841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T03:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b955d20c9185e7c50d81d8341dd4d8e633cdec1","tid":580963,"